Package: mars
Title: Multivariate Adaptive Regression Splines
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Akaaljot", "Mathoda", email = "asm40@sfu.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Mayank", "Mayank", email = "mma266@sfu.ca", role = "aut"))
Description: Implements the MARS algorithm of Friedman (1991) for
    flexible nonlinear regression using piecewise-linear hinge basis
    functions with forward stepwise construction and backward pruning
    via generalized cross-validation.
